            "height": 428,
            "content": "## Property Inquiry → Personalized SMS + AI Buyer Qualification\n\n**How it works:**\n1. Receives property inquiry from Zillow, Realtor.com, IDX site, or Facebook Lead Ads\n2. Normalizes buyer data + property address, price, and MLS#\n3. Creates contact in Aloware with full property details in custom fields\n4. Sends hyper-personalized SMS referencing the exact property\n5. Enrolls in AI Buyer Qualification Sequence\n\n**Setup:**\n- Set n8n Variables: `ALOWARE_API_TOKEN`, `ALOWARE_LINE_PHONE`, `ALOWARE_SEQUENCE_ID`, `AGENT_NAME`, `BROKERAGE_NAME`\n- Connect your lead source to POST to this webhook URL\n- Create an AI Buyer Qualification Sequence in Aloware"
          },
